===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|φώνημα||tr=phōnēma||sound|lang=grc}}, from {{term|φωνέω||tr=phōneō||to sound|lang=grc}}, from {{term|φωνή||tr=phōnē||sound|lang=grc}}.

