* {{a|US}} {{enPR|fōn'ēm}}, {{IPA|/ˈfoʊˌnim/}}
* {{audio|En-us-phoneme.ogg|Audio (US)}}

* {{hyphenation|pho|neme|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|linguistics|lang=en}} An indivisible [[unit]] of [[sound]] in a given language. A phoneme is an abstraction of the physical speech sounds ([[phone]]s) and may encompass several different phones.

